title: From The Archives: Local Babies on CBS Sitcom Lenny
text: 5:19 pm Chattanooga (WDEF) - We celebrate the new fall TV season with this look back at a new CBS show in 1990.The didn't turn out to be a hit.But it did mark the TV debut of a pair of young actresses from Chattanooga... very young.Rachel and Kathleen tag teamed to play the baby in the family sitcom.And they had some proud grandparents watching back home in Chattanooga.Here is the story by Ted Perry in 1990 From the Archives.
